A popular Nigerian singer, Ayodeji Ibrahim Balogun, aka Wizkid, has revealed something he just discovered. According to the 29 year old, the president of Nigeria, Muhammadu Buhari and the president of America, Donald Trump are the same person. He however mentioned that the different between the two is that Donald Trump is active on Twitter while Buhari is not. His tweet reads ; “Buhari/Trump same person lol only difference be say one sabi use twitter pass the other. Clueless!” Buhari/Trump same person lol only difference be say one sabi use twitter pass the other. Clueless!